Major Features: â€¢ Promise Tracker with community submission workflow â€¢ Civic Memory Board with verification system â€¢ Content algorithm implementation and testing â€¢ Experience Points (XP) system with civic rewards
Phase 3: Learning & Access (Months 4-6)
